Welcome!

This is the distribution for the Tachikoma distributed messaging system.

To get started, follow the instructions in the file INSTALL.

or, from this directory, simply run:

  bin/install_tachikoma

Then:

  tachikoma-server
  tachikoma-client

At the prompt, type "help" for a list of possible commands.  You might want
to start with "connect server_log".

Have fun with your new Tachikoma!

